\fs36 \cf0 Product Overview\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Wealth helps The Arabic-speaking public in Kuwait and the GCC seeking trusted health and treatment news, plus healthcare professionals, hospital administrators, investors, and policymakers following the sector. by solving: In Kuwait and the GCC, there's no trusted source for what's happening in the health sector \'97 new medications and treatments, doctor movements, clinical breakthroughs, and what's entering the market. Health news is scattered or buried in rumors. This platform becomes the first reference for credible, simplified health news \'97 including the sector's economic developments. The core AI capability is: AI monitors trusted international sources \'97 Reuters, BBC, leading medical schools, WHO, and CDC \'97 then summarizes and simplifies complex medical news into clear, accurate Arabic content. It generates articles, headlines, and social captions in multiple variations, drafts newsletter digests, and flags unverified or exaggerated claims before publishing..\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

